{"tid":2104413,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"（國難五金回應）講個笑話你聽，初選","createTime":"2020-07-12T02:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T09:27:26.000Z","uid":11256,"like":12,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e4179e7749e31fe3fa3ac70fb2eaa181621dd2af","tid":2104413,"uid":11256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"越係走得前嘅人就越痛苦，當年五區公投全民制憲有成50萬人投票，嗰啲叫唔叫民意？<br />\n<br />\n今日為咗俾大家睇吓所謂嘅民意，搞咁大場大龍鳳出嚟，到頭來對呢個政權完全冇任何影響，根本就係成班香港人喺度集體打飛機。<br />\n<br />\n高潮過後～<br />\n再一次俾人DQ<br />\n再一次宣布民主最黑暗嘅一日<br />\n再一次over my dead body<br />\n大白象工程撥款繼續通過<br />\n擠壓市民嘅條例繼續繞過立法會<br />\n<br />\n仲好意思覺得初選就叫做付出？<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講乜嘢叫支線，主線都停咗落嚟嘅時候，你做乜撚嘢都係多餘嘅咋。<br />\n<br />\n圖片：端傳媒"},{"pid":"7dab69ef87e19bbdcc31595c271a5b200bcc8ed6","tid":2104413,"uid":11256,"like":28,"dislike":5,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:56:39.000Z","msg":"膠都廢事比國難五金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd39533e36b6b0b0bb155c434605d8608a3320b","tid":2104413,"uid":94824,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f2e142fb2e2aea5fb74d51479752b36d8b3281","tid":2104413,"uid":312223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:04:47.000Z","msg":"當慣性公投出現  成件事就會唔同哂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"